
Beautifly	 A bug type Pokémon

BEAUTIFLY’s favorite food is 
the sweet pollen of flowers. 
 If you want to see Beautifly, 
just leave a potted flower by 
an open window.  BEAUTIFLY is 
sure to come looking for pollen. 

